<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>中国茶文化 - 茶之道</title>
    <div id="banner">
        <!-- 替换下面的src为你的图片链接 -->
        <img src="http://www.chawh.net/images/tea_02.gif" alt="茶文化网横幅">
    <style>
        body, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(#eef5c2, #d0f4d0);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        #banner img { width: 100%; height: auto; }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: '楷体', cursive;
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #006400;
        }

        .navbar {
            background: rgb(236, 244, 180);
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .navbar a {
            display: inline-block;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        a:hover{
			background: linear-gradient(#f5f5f4, #aee2fd);
            color: #333;
        }
        .tea-category {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .tea-box {
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #f0c1ec, #b0d9ef);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            width: calc(33.333% - 20px);
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .tea-box h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .tea-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .tea-list li {
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .tea-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        footer {
            background: #f5f5dc; /* 页脚浅黄色背景 */
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

    <div class="header">
        <h1 class="logo">茶之道</h1>
        <div class="navbar">
            <a href="/" class="active">茶学首页</a>
            <a href="/culture/">茶学文化</a>
            <a href="/category/">茶叶分类</a>
            <a href="/products/">茶叶产品</a>
            <a href="/market/">茶市行情售卖</a>
        </div>
    </div>

